==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bloated
<hw>Bloat"ed</hw> <pr>(bl⟦omac⟧t"⟦ecr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>p. a.</pos>
<def>Distended beyond the natural or usual size, as by the presence of
water, serum, etc.; turgid; swollen; <as>as, a <ex>bloated</ex>
face</as>. Also, puffed up with pride; pompous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bloatedness</ent>⟦br⟧
